00:24:20,755 --> 00:24:21,870
Fais attention, Jack.

453
00:24:21,926 --> 00:24:23,831
Merci, Sam.

454
00:24:32,097 --> 00:24:33,052
Oui.

455
00:24:33,145 --> 00:24:34,721
C'est Liddy.

456
00:24:34,805 --> 00:24:36,183
Tu ne devineras jamais qui vient juste d'appeler.

457
00:24:36,268 --> 00:24:37,220
Qui ça?

458
00:24:37,318 --> 00:24:38,392
Ton frère, Jack.

459
00:24:38,477 --> 00:24:40,061
De quoi parles-tu?

